Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Boycotts can backfire
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xb07
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 16 Oct 1983
When the oldest form of retaliation - the boycott - turns out to have unforeseen consquences which hit home markets hardest. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less